Package: rstansim
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Running Simulation Studies With Stan And R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ewan", "Keith", email = "ewan.keith100@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <ewan.keith100@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a wrapper function for fitting a
    stan model to multiple data sets, then extracting and
    combining specified estimates from all models. Allows for
    Nested parallelism across simulation runs and stan chains.
